Singleton (1970), ^Inf~. 34.62                    Doc 32 of 37, Screen  1

[Copyrighted Material] |Giuda Scariotto~: Judas Iscariot, the betrayer of      
Christ, who thus occupies the position of "honor" in Hell, and for whom this   
last subdivision of the ninth circle is named (see vs. 117).  See ^Inf.~ XIX,  
96, where Judas is called "the guilty soul."                                   
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
