Singleton (1970), ^Inf~. 34.64                    Doc 33 of 37, Screen  1

[Copyrighted Material] |hanno il capo di sotto~: The other two sinners dangle  
by the feet from the other two mouths of Satan, their heads hanging down.      
This apparently is a lesser punishment than that suffered by Judas, who has    
his head in the mouth and his feet hanging down.                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
